Name: Nov 6, 2017 - Roasted Veggie Quinoa Salad
Short description: Roasted seasonal vegetables tossed with tender quinoa in a balsamic-dijon vinaigrette. Served with a house made pumpkin muffin, and vine-ripened seasonal fruit.

Name: Nov 3, 2017 - Chicken Salad Wrap or White Bean Wrap
Short description: *Meat Option* Roasted free range chicken mixed with organic celery, organic carrots, crasins, and mayonnaise, then wrapped in a soft flour tortilla. *Vegetarian Option* Tender white beans mixed with organic celery, organic carrots, crasins and mayonnaise and wrapped in a soft flour tortilla. Served with organic cucumber slices, house-made ranch dressing and vine-ripened seasonal fruit.
